text: Zeta Cephei is a red supergiant star located in the constellation Cepheus. It has a diameter 94 times that of the Sun and a temperature of more than 4,000 degrees Kelvin.https://arxiv.org/abs/1905.03744 It is located 840 light years away from Earth.https://arxiv.org/abs/0708.1752 == References == Category:Supergiants Category:red giants Category:Stars
